title: The Amazing Spider-Man v1.1.9 FULL
description:
====================================================================================
Name:      The Amazing Spider-Man
Version:   1.1.9
Category:  Action and Adventure
Developer: Gameloft 
Price:     $0,99
====================================================================================


Get ready for intense action to fling your web, with The Amazing Spider-Man! Join him in the official game of this highly anticipated success of 2012! Play the film's plot, while Spider-Man confronts the Lizard and gangs in turmoil. Throws your web and move you through New York open and in full 3D, while using your amazing abilities to save the town.



                                  2014[YahSoft]
